---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About" description="whoami" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="noise"></div>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <aside class="sys-info">
        <h2>./sys_specs</h2>
        <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">usr:</span><span class="spec-val">muhaiman ali shah</span></div>
        <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">loc:</span><span class="spec-val">pakistan</span></div>
        <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">stack:</span><span class="spec-val">js, next.js, tailwind</span></div>
        <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">os:</span><span class="spec-val">linux (mentally)</span></div>
        <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">status:</span><span class="spec-val">building devsafar</span></div>
      </aside>

      <section class="bio-section">
        <h1>cat about.md</h1>
        <p>i am a developer building out of pakistan. this space is my digital notebook, a public ledger of everything i am learning, breaking, and fixing.</p>
        <div class="block-quote">"seekhte seekhte sikhana." <br />(teaching while still learning.)</div>
        <p>if you are just starting out, maybe something in these logs will help you compile your own thoughts.</p>
        <div class="contact-cmds">
          <div class="cmd-line"><span>// drop an email:</span> <a href="mailto:muhaiman@example.com">ping --mail muhaiman</a></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  main {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 5rem 5vw;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .sys-info {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem;
    height: fit-content;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);
  }
  .sys-info h2 { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--neon); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .spec-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .spec-key { color: var(--muted); }
  .spec-val { color: var(--text); }

  .bio-section h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }
  .bio-section h1::before { content: "> "; color: var(--neon); }
  .bio-section p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .block-quote {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--neon);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #888;
  }
  .contact-cmds { margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px dashed var(--border); }
  .cmd-line { font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .cmd-line span { color: var(--muted); margin-right: 1rem; }
  .cmd-line a { color: var(--neon); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed transparent; transition: border 0.2s; }
  .cmd-line a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--neon); }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .sys-info { order: 2; }
    .bio-section { order: 1; }
  }
</style>